amazon global selling organization. our vision is to transform global commerce by bringing selection from around the world to customers anywhere in the world, you will set strategy , policy, build processes, evangelize for technology solutions that allow third party sellers from all over the world to bring hundreds of millions of new items to amazon's 11 marketplaces worldwide. you will determine what experience these sellers must offer our customers, create the incentives , management of global programs , stakeholders, driving alignment for new programs at high levels of the organization. this position will also have management responsibility for product managers, data analysts, an operations team. from jeff bezos' annual letter to amazon shareholders: "to further globalize marketplace, in countries where we don't have a presence - reach out to our customers in countries outside their home geographies. we hosted merchants from more than 100 different countries last year, helped them connect with customers in 185 nations. almost one-fifth of our overall third-party sales now occur outside the sellers' home countries, our merchants' cross-border sales nearly doubled last year. in the eu, manage their business in multiple languages, make products available across our five eu websites. more recently, helping them obtain ocean shipping from asia to europe , bulk rates." fulfillment by amazon fba is an amazon service for our third-party sellers. the fba team partners with sellers , we are changing lives with the work we do. our fba employees wake up every day thinking about how to enable our sellers to be successful on our platform. enabling seller success allows us to provide amazon customers with unparalleled selection , a win for customers. want to learn more about fba? ? seller's success stories: sellersuccess ? a free book of stories from small businesses, sellers, authors, , innovators that are thriving on amazon: transformations-ebook
